<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>Log in to Solstice Cloud at <a href="../../PDF/Solstice_22Miles_Digital_Signage.pdf/#https://cloud.mersive.com/">https://cloud.mersive.com/</a>.</li>
            <li>Go to <b>Manage</b> &gt; <b>Pods</b> and click the name of the Pod you want to display 22Miles Digital Signage content on.</li>
            <li>Scroll down and click the down arrow to expand the <b>Digital Signage</b> settings.</li>
            <li>Check <b>Enable Digital Signage</b> and select a display mode.</li>
            <li>In <b>Source URL</b>, enter the URL for the 22Miles digital signage device, which should look similar to the following: http://h5.22miles.com/wl/[shortcode from 22Miles]</li>
            <li>Click <b>Save as Unassigned</b>, or you can <b>Save as New Template</b> to create a digital signage template you can apply to multiple Pods. Any Pod assigned this digital signage template will display the content assigned to that 22Miles device URL.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>